{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.1","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:1","prev_osis_id":"Deut.003.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortation<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-24: cf. (v. 32-40. De 6:1-15; 5:1-22. Jos 23:6-8, 16.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Maintenant, Isra\u00ebl, \u00e9coute les lois et les ordonnances que je vous enseigne. Mettez-les en pratique, afin que vous viviez, et que vous entriez en possession du pays que vous donne l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de vos p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.3.29","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 3:29","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.3.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.2","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:2","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Vous n\u2019ajouterez rien \u00e0 ce que je vous prescris, et vous n\u2019en retrancherez rien; mais vous observerez les commandements de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, tels que je vous les prescris.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.3","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:3","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Vos yeux ont vu ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel a fait \u00e0 l\u2019occasion de Baal-Peor: l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, a d\u00e9truit du milieu de toi tous ceux qui \u00e9taient all\u00e9s apr\u00e8s Baal-Peor.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.4","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:4","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et vous, qui vous \u00eates attach\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, vous \u00eates aujourd\u2019hui tous vivants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.5","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:5","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Voici, je vous ai enseign\u00e9 des lois et des ordonnances, comme l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mon Dieu, me l\u2019a command\u00e9, afin que vous les mettiez en pratique dans le pays dont vous allez prendre possession.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.6","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:6","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Vous les observerez et vous les mettrez en pratique; car ce sera l\u00e0 votre sagesse et votre intelligence aux yeux des peuples, qui entendront parler de toutes ces lois et qui diront: Cette grande nation est un peuple absolument sage et intelligent!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.7","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:7","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Quelle est, en effet, la grande nation qui ait des dieux aussi proches que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, l\u2019est de nous toutes les fois que nous l\u2019invoquons?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.8","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:8","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et quelle est la grande nation qui ait des lois et des ordonnances justes, comme toute cette loi que je vous pr\u00e9sente aujourd\u2019hui?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.9","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:9","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Seulement, prends garde \u00e0 toi et veille attentivement sur ton \u00e2me, tous les jours de ta vie, de peur que tu n\u2019oublies les choses que tes yeux ont vues, et qu\u2019elles ne sortent de ton c\u0153ur; enseigne-les \u00e0 tes enfants et aux enfants de tes enfants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.10","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:10","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Souviens-toi du jour o\u00f9 tu te pr\u00e9sentas devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, \u00e0 Horeb, lorsque l\u2019\u00c9ternel me dit: Assemble aupr\u00e8s de moi le peuple! Je veux leur faire entendre mes paroles, afin qu\u2019ils apprennent \u00e0 me craindre tout le temps qu\u2019ils vivront sur la terre; et afin qu\u2019ils les enseignent \u00e0 leurs enfants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.11","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:11","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Vous vous approch\u00e2tes et vous vous t\u00eentes au pied de la montagne. La montagne \u00e9tait embras\u00e9e, et les flammes s\u2019\u00e9levaient jusqu\u2019au milieu du ciel. Il y avait des t\u00e9n\u00e8bres, des nu\u00e9es, de l\u2019obscurit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.12","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:12","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Et l\u2019\u00c9ternel vous parla du milieu du feu; vous entend\u00eetes le son des paroles, mais vous ne v\u00eetes point de figure, vous n\u2019entend\u00eetes qu\u2019une voix.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.13","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:13","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Il publia son alliance, qu\u2019il vous ordonna d\u2019observer, les dix commandements; et il les \u00e9crivit sur deux tables de pierre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.14","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:14","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>En ce temps-l\u00e0, l\u2019\u00c9ternel me commanda de vous enseigner des lois et des ordonnances, afin que vous les mettiez en pratique dans le pays dont vous allez prendre possession.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.15","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:15","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Puisque vous n\u2019avez vu aucune figure le jour o\u00f9 l\u2019\u00c9ternel vous parla du milieu du feu, \u00e0 Horeb, veillez attentivement sur vos \u00e2mes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.16","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:16","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>de peur que vous ne vous corrompiez et que vous ne vous fassiez une image taill\u00e9e, une repr\u00e9sentation de quelque idole, la figure d\u2019un homme ou d\u2019une femme,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.17","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:17","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>la figure d\u2019un animal qui soit sur la terre, la figure d\u2019un oiseau qui vole dans les cieux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.18","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.18","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:18","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>la figure d\u2019une b\u00eate qui rampe sur le sol, la figure d\u2019un poisson qui vive dans les eaux au-dessous de la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.19","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.19","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:19","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Veille sur ton \u00e2me, de peur que, levant tes yeux vers le ciel, et voyant le soleil, la lune et les \u00e9toiles, toute l\u2019arm\u00e9e des cieux, tu ne sois entra\u00een\u00e9 \u00e0 te prosterner en leur pr\u00e9sence et \u00e0 leur rendre un culte: ce sont des choses que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, a donn\u00e9es en partage \u00e0 tous les peuples, sous le ciel tout entier.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.20","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.18","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.20","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:20","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Mais vous, l\u2019\u00c9ternel vous a pris, et vous a fait sortir de la fournaise de fer de l\u2019\u00c9gypte, afin que vous fussiez un peuple qui lui appart\u00eent en propre, comme vous l\u2019\u00eates aujourd\u2019hui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.21","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.19","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.21","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:21","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et l\u2019\u00c9ternel s\u2019irrita contre moi, \u00e0 cause de vous; et il jura que je ne passerais point le Jourdain, et que je n\u2019entrerais point dans le bon pays que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, te donne en h\u00e9ritage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.20","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.22","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:22","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Je mourrai donc en ce pays-ci, je ne passerai point le Jourdain; mais vous le passerez, et vous poss\u00e9derez ce bon pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.23","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.21","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.23","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:23","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Veillez sur vous, afin de ne point mettre en oubli l\u2019alliance que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, a trait\u00e9e avec vous, et de ne point vous faire d\u2019image taill\u00e9e, de repr\u00e9sentation quelconque, que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, t\u2019ait d\u00e9fendue.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.24","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:24","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Car l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, est un feu d\u00e9vorant, un Dieu jaloux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.25","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.23","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.25","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:25","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.026,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 25-31: cf. De 29:18-28; 30:1-10, 15-18. L\u00e9 26:39-45. (Lu 15:16-24.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Lorsque tu auras des enfants, et des enfants de tes enfants, et que vous serez depuis longtemps dans le pays, si vous vous corrompez, si vous faites des images taill\u00e9es, des repr\u00e9sentations de quoi que ce soit, si vous faites ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, pour l\u2019irriter,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.26","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.26","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:26","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>j\u2019en prends aujourd\u2019hui \u00e0 t\u00e9moin contre vous le ciel et la terre, vous dispara\u00eetrez par une mort rapide du pays dont vous allez prendre possession au-del\u00e0 du Jourdain, vous n\u2019y prolongerez pas vos jours, car vous serez enti\u00e8rement d\u00e9truits.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.27","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.25","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.27","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:27","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel vous dispersera parmi les peuples, et vous ne resterez qu\u2019un petit nombre au milieu des nations o\u00f9 l\u2019\u00c9ternel vous emm\u00e8nera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.28","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.26","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.28","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:28","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Et l\u00e0, vous servirez des dieux, ouvrage de mains d\u2019homme, du bois et de la pierre, qui ne peuvent ni voir, ni entendre, ni manger, ni sentir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.29","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.27","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.29","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:29","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>C\u2019est de l\u00e0 aussi que tu chercheras l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, et que tu le trouveras, si tu le cherches de tout ton c\u0153ur et de toute ton \u00e2me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.30","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.28","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.30","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:30","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Au sein de ta d\u00e9tresse, toutes ces choses t\u2019arriveront. Alors, dans la suite des temps, tu retourneras \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, et tu \u00e9couteras sa voix;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.31","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.29","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.31","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:31","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>car l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, est un Dieu de mis\u00e9ricorde, qui ne t\u2019abandonnera point et ne te d\u00e9truira point: il n\u2019oubliera pas l\u2019alliance de tes p\u00e8res, qu\u2019il leur a jur\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.32","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.30","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.32","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:32","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.033,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 32-40: cf. (De 6:20-25; 5:22-29.) (De 7:7-11; 11:1-9, 22-25; 33:29.) Ps 29:1-11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Interroge les temps anciens qui t\u2019ont pr\u00e9c\u00e9d\u00e9, depuis le jour o\u00f9 Dieu cr\u00e9a l\u2019homme sur la terre, et d\u2019une extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 du ciel \u00e0 l\u2019autre: y eut-il jamais si grand \u00e9v\u00e9nement, et a-t-on jamais ou\u00ef chose semblable?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.33","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.31","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.33","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:33","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Fut-il jamais un peuple qui entend\u00eet la voix de Dieu parlant du milieu du feu, comme tu l\u2019as entendue, et qui soit demeur\u00e9 vivant?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.34","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.32","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.34","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:34","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Fut-il jamais un dieu qui essay\u00e2t de venir prendre \u00e0 lui une nation du milieu d\u2019une nation, par des \u00e9preuves, des signes, des miracles et des combats, \u00e0 main forte et \u00e0 bras \u00e9tendu, et avec des prodiges de terreur, comme l\u2019a fait pour vous l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, en \u00c9gypte et sous vos yeux?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.35","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.33","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.35","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:35","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Tu as \u00e9t\u00e9 rendu t\u00e9moin de ces choses, afin que tu reconnusses que l\u2019\u00c9ternel est Dieu, qu\u2019il n\u2019y en a point d\u2019autre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.36","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:36","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.34","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.36","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:36","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Du ciel, il t\u2019a fait entendre sa voix pour t\u2019instruire; et, sur la terre, il t\u2019a fait voir son grand feu, et tu as entendu ses paroles du milieu du feu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.37","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:37","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.35","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.37","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:37","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Il a aim\u00e9 tes p\u00e8res, et il a choisi leur post\u00e9rit\u00e9 apr\u00e8s eux; il t\u2019a fait lui-m\u00eame sortir d\u2019\u00c9gypte par sa grande puissance;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.38","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:38","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.36","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:36","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.38","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:38","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>il a chass\u00e9 devant toi des nations sup\u00e9rieures en nombre et en force, pour te faire entrer dans leur pays, pour t\u2019en donner la possession, comme tu le vois aujourd\u2019hui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.39","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:39","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.37","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:37","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.39","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:39","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Sache donc en ce jour, et retiens dans ton c\u0153ur que l\u2019\u00c9ternel est Dieu, en haut dans le ciel et en bas sur la terre, et qu\u2019il n\u2019y en a point d\u2019autre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.40","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:40","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.38","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:38","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.40","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:40","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Et observe ses lois et ses commandements que je te prescris aujourd\u2019hui, afin que tu sois heureux, toi et tes enfants apr\u00e8s toi, et que tu prolonges d\u00e9sormais tes jours dans le pays que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, te donne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.41","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:41","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.39","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:39","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.41","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:41","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.042,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 41-43: cf. (De 19:1-10. Jos 20.) Ex 21:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>\n    Alors Mo\u00efse choisit trois villes de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9 du Jourdain, \u00e0 l\u2019orient,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.42","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:42","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.40","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:40","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.42","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:42","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>afin qu\u2019elles servissent de refuge au meurtrier qui aurait involontairement tu\u00e9 son prochain, sans avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 auparavant son ennemi, et afin qu\u2019il p\u00fbt sauver sa vie en s\u2019enfuyant dans l\u2019une de ces villes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.43","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:43","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.41","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:41","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.43","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:43","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>C\u2019\u00e9taient: Betser, dans le d\u00e9sert, dans la plaine, chez les Rub\u00e9nites; Ramoth, en Galaad, chez les Gadites, et Golan, en Basan, chez les Manassites.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.44","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:44","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.42","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:42","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.44","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:44","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.045,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le D\u00e9calogue r\u00e9p\u00e9t\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">4 v. 44 \u00e0 5 v. 21: cf. (Ex 19:1, etc.; 20:1-17.) 2 Pi 1:12-15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>C\u2019est ici la loi que pr\u00e9senta Mo\u00efse aux enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.45","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:45","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.43","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:43","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.45","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:45","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup>Voici les pr\u00e9ceptes, les lois et les ordonnances que Mo\u00efse prescrivit aux enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, apr\u00e8s leur sortie d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.46","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:46","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.44","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:44","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.46","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:46","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.047,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup>C\u2019\u00e9tait de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9 du Jourdain, dans la vall\u00e9e, vis-\u00e0-vis de Beth-Peor, au pays de Sihon, roi des Amor\u00e9ens, qui habitait \u00e0 Hesbon, et qui fut battu par Mo\u00efse et les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, apr\u00e8s leur sortie d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.47","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:47","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.45","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:45","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.47","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:47","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup>Ils s\u2019empar\u00e8rent de son pays et de celui d\u2019Og, roi de Basan. Ces deux rois des Amor\u00e9ens \u00e9taient de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9 du Jourdain, \u00e0 l\u2019orient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.48","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:48","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.46","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:46","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.48","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:48","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.004.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup>Leur territoire s\u2019\u00e9tendait depuis Aro\u00ebr sur les bords du torrent de l\u2019Arnon jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la montagne de Sion qui est l\u2019Hermon,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.49","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:49","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.47","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:47","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.49","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:49","prev_osis_id":"Deut.004.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.4.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup>et il embrassait toute la plaine de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9 du Jourdain, \u00e0 l\u2019orient, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la mer de la plaine, au pied du Pisga.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.5.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.4.48","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 4:48","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.4.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb876cad4.72719143');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb876cad4.72719143\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb876cad4.72719143","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb876cad4.72719143'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb876cad4.72719143\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}